spec_data.Name: ipxe-roms-qemu
spec_data.License: GPLv2 with additional permissions and BSD
spec_data.Description:
iPXE is an open source network bootloader. It provides a direct
replacement for proprietary PXE ROMs, with many extra features such as
DNS, HTTP, iSCSI, etc.

This package contains the iPXE ROMs for devices emulated by QEMU, in
.rom format.

spec_data.Summary: Network boot loader roms supported by QEMU, .rom format
